To create the full chain that nginx requires combine the following keys/certs. Order matters:

-----BEGIN RSA PRIVATE KEY----- 
(Your Private Key: example_com.key) 
-----END RSA PRIVATE KEY----- 
-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE----- 
(Your Primary SSL certificate: example_com.crt) 
-----END CERTIFICATE----- 
-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE----- 
(Your Intermediate certificate: DigiCertCA.crt) 
-----END CERTIFICATE----- 
-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE----- 
(Your Root certificate: TrustedRoot.crt) 
-----END CERTIFICATE-----
